                <head>271. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d271fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Affairs, Staff Material, Office File, Meetings File, Box 21, <gloss
                            target="#t_SCC_1">SCC</gloss> Meeting #313, Held 5/15/80, 5/80. Secret.
                            <persName corresp="#p_CJE_1">Carter</persName> initialed “C” in the top
